{"body": "So this line is what's causing the problem:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/actionview/test/abstract_unit.rb#L7\r\n\r\nIf we stop explicitly telling ruby where to put the tmpdir it will just create it in your systems tmp directory and everything runs fine. I'm not really sure why that is though or why we are explicitly telling ruby where to put the tmpdir.\r\n\r\nThere's also another instance of overriding the tmpdir here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/actionpack/test/abstract_unit.rb#L7\r\n\r\nWhat do you guys think about just stopping overriding the tmpdir?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/22076778", "created_at": "2013-08-04T18:59:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11743#issuecomment-22076778", "updated_at": "2013-08-04T18:59:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11743, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/atambo", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/302c6c56b99912a673f1213b0709c902?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F5c40637db9e64b69d4e949dd3f79b312.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/received_events", "gravatar_id": "302c6c56b99912a673f1213b0709c902", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "atambo", "type": "User", "id": 102009, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/atambo/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d1a1bd3543c151007df5"}, "id": 22076778, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/